_sText:
Awp_freeway

This is a "big" size map (I call it AWP sized) that is centered around a set of freeway onramps.  There is an overpass that crosses above the freeway.  Players can jump over the center dividers to get to the other side as well.  Because of the size of the map, some aesthetics were left out in order to improve FPS.  

All players start with the following equipment:  AWP sniper rifle, Deagle pistol, Knife, and Kevlar vest. There are no buy zones.

- 52 Spawn Points, 26 per team
- No Buy Zones
- Nav File for bots
- Overview radar map included
- 3d Skybox
- All files compiled into the bsp using Pakrat

Happy Sniping!

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
